        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks for <hi rend="italic">Movement in plants</hi>. Praises the terms CD introduces, but criticises CD’s use of the teleological word "purpose".</p> 
            <p>Outlines his efforts to study the inheritance of characters in his family. F. Galton overemphasises the inheritance of good qualities.</p>
        </abstract>
